	&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/image/data/banner/canin-size-chart.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 760px; height: 324px;&quot; /&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;width:192px;position:absolute;top:25px; left:14px;font:bold 18px/22px 'Arial';color:white;text-align: left;letter-spacing:1px;display:block;&quot;&gt;To obtain the correct Hidez suit size for your Racing Greyhound simply compare your greyhound&amp;#39;s weight to HIDEZ size chart.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font: bold 25px/30px 'Arial'; color: black; width: 90%; text-align: center; position: absolute; top: 5px; display: block;&quot;&gt;Racing Greyhound&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
";}i:8;a:7:{s:14:"information_id";s:2:"36";s:6:"bottom";s:1:"0";s:10:"sort_order";s:1:"3";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:11:"language_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:17:"Canine Size-Chart";s:11:"description";s:678:"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;display:black;position:relative;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/image/data/banner/canin-size-chart.jpg&quot; /&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;width:260px;position:absolute;top:55px; left:14px;font:bold 18px/22px 'Arial';color:white;text-align: left;letter-spacing:1px;display:block;&quot;&gt;To obtain the correct Hidez suit size for your Racing Greyhound simply compare your greyhound&amp;#39;s weight to HIDEZ size chart.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font: bold 25px/30px 'Arial'; color: black; width: 90%; text-align: center; position: absolute; top: 5px; display: block;&quot;&gt;Racing Greyhound&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
