";}i:18;a:7:{s:14:"information_id";s:1:"9";s:6:"bottom";s:1:"0";s:10:"sort_order";s:1:"3";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:11:"language_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:21:"Equine How To Measure";s:11:"description";s:1271:"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
	To&amp;nbsp;Obtain the correct Hidez suit size for your horse, simply measure the height of your horse from the ground level to the highest point of the horse&amp;#39;s withers. Then refer to the Hidez size chart.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin: 0px auto; width: 648px; text-align: center; position: relative;&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div style=&quot;font: bold 26px/26px &amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;; top: 17px; width: 648px; text-align: center; color: white; position: absolute; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;&quot;&gt;
		HOW TO MEASURE YOUR HORSE&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;img alt=&quot;horse size chart&quot; src=&quot;/image/data/infomartion/horse_size.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width: 648px; height: 590px;&quot; /&gt;
	&lt;div style=&quot;font: bold 14px/18px &amp;quot;Arial&amp;quot;; left: 82px; width: 490px; text-align: left; bottom: 27px; color: white; position: absolute; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal;&quot;&gt;
		To obtain the correct &lt;span&gt;HIDEZ&lt;/span&gt; suit size for your hourse,simply measure the height of your horse from the ground level to the highest point of the horse&amp;#39;s withers.Then refer to &lt;span&gt;HIDEZ&lt;/span&gt; size chart&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
";}i:19;a:7:{s:14:"information_id";s:2:"10";s:6:"bottom";s:1:"0";s:10:"sort_order";s:1:"3";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:11:"language_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:17:"Equine Size-Chart";s:11:"description";s:6021:"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
	Below is the size chart for the Hidez EQUINE compression recovery suits. Please find the correct size to fit your horses.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
	If you are unaware on how to measure your horse, &lt;a href=&quot;/skin/common_files/images/size-chart.jpg&quot;&gt;please click here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table class=&quot;size-table&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;th width=&quot;250&quot;&gt;
				DESCRIPTION&lt;/th&gt;
			&lt;th&gt;
				HANDS&lt;/th&gt;
			&lt;th&gt;
				INCHES&lt;/th&gt;
			&lt;th&gt;
				CENTIMETRES&lt;/th&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;th rowspan=&quot;4&quot;&gt;
				MINIATURE&lt;/th&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				6.2 H&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				26-28 inches&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				66-70 cm&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				7 H&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				28-30 inches&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				71-75 cm&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;
				7.2 H&lt;/td&gt;
