	&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Supply and Delivery of your purchase&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Your purchase will be delivered FREE worldwide by International Express Courier to your nominated address&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Please ensure that the shipping address you enter is correct.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Delivery of your package will be by International Express Courier. For In stock products ( Black , Blue, and Red suits &amp;nbsp;)&amp;nbsp;please allow 5-6 business days.For special make-up products ,such as Printed suits and Custom Designed suits( after final artwork approval)&amp;nbsp;which are made to order please allow 14 business days&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	You can check your order status at any time under the &amp;ldquo;my account&amp;rdquo; section when you login as a member to the Website.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	Unless otherwise stated orders will be delivered during normal business hours between 8am and 5pm and need to be signed for. It is a good idea to enter a delivery address at which someone will be present to accept the goods at this time; for example your workplace. If there is no one present at the delivery location who is entitled to accept and sign for the delivery, a card will be left in your letterbox informing you about the incomplete delivery and where to pick your parcels up.&amp;nbsp;In cases where the parcel is returned to Hidez Pty Ltd due to either not being picked up or an incorrect delivery address, we will refund the purchase price but not the delivery charges. If the product has been damaged in transfer, please inform Hidez Pty Ltd immediately and provide pictures. .&lt;/p&gt;
